---
title: Tijuana-Style Pork Tenderloin & Feta Tacos with Slaw, Guacamole & Charred Pineapple
description: Spiced is nice and fresh is best, that’s our motto for making up these Mexican-style tacos. Spiced pork does the trick to make your mouth water and the classic addition of guacamole is a must. Bring in the fresh taste of summer with charred pineapple and you’re good to go!
